Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me off of this mission, Ms McCunnen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something important to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was something more important than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:01:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This is your passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real you... your past is written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could've known...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about the twist of the fate that was waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid of regaining your past?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been following the organization's orders to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You've had great achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to kill them because I had no past and memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been following orders like a robot without feeling any guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you regain your original self,\Nyou might be tormented by your sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid of that, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's precisely why I want you to return to your former self.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my own will...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance is 249 yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An intermittent strong wind is blowing from the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to your true self, and accept yourself as Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your organization was the one that took away my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was also the organization\Nthat stained my hands with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization will be reborn soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be there, Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how skilled you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a doll who only follows its orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dependable subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who will follow me of his own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I learn about my past...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not confident that I can keep going as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that time comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mission is to back up the raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people in sight are my targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which organization are they from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lading...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sniper?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to say that, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to nail us down here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try reading your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you remembered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've killed so many people with these hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I wanted to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was better off not knowing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up from your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll return to being you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept your past and your sins and face them with your own will,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuma Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Scythe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone who needs your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.11,0:08:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're willing to stain your hands with blood again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and share your guilt with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to show you a wonderful life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I'm not forcing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make the other choice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other choice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might doubt me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll really allow you to go back to your hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I want is a subordinate with a solid will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you shooting your allies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be Scythe's order but stop acting like a puppet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That snaky bastard is just using you as a disposable pawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important decision for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.23,0:10:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some time to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? This is the Azuma residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Scythe bastard betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear how many people she killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall repay him suitably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Phantom as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come here to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then hurry up and return to the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a sudden change of plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe betrayed the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made Phantom attack Inferno's lading.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he immersed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phantom has escaped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But luckily Lizzie shot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization is looking for those two with all their might.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't found either of them though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They suspect that you've deserted the organization, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can give you an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you don't have any time to consider my deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.74,0:13:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a decision quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my side...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe and Phantom are our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're with them, the organization will...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.33,0:14:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bleeding won't stop.\NThe bullet didn't pass through all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to take her to a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.23,0:14:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The organization probably has connections to hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die on me, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We sealed off all possible escape routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're literally birds in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can run away from the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who will hunt the prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't find them with so many people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Highway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God damn it! If I had just killed her there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clau, what about him? {Title 6, Chapter 342 - Clau}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zwei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Scythe's pet dog, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite possible that he'd be on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, Lizzie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...shall kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms McCunnen gave me my passport tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My passport...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I remembered everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About my hometown, my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.87,0:17:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even remembered my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuma Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's much better than a boring name like Zwei, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer my old self.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I only return to the organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein... we should both go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe and Phantom are our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're with them, the organization will... kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go back, Ein will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave Ein here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and go back alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.45,0:19:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue, white, and green.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.81,0:19:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's so bright there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the wind is blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A very strong wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.95,0:19:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without having a name, we were just given numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just used like pawns and abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.58,0:20:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has to be a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This meaningless way of life has to be a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ein,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forsake you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't hand you over to the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape together, Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Phantom nor a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.88,0:23:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your own name...
